\c 20
\s Mvura yeMeribha
\p
\v 1 Ipapo vana vaIsraeri, ungano yose, vakasvika murenje reZini nemwedzi wekutanga; vanhu ndokugara muKadheshi\x + 33.36.Num. 13.21.\x*; Miriami ndokufirapo, ndokuvigwapo\x + Eki. 15.20. Num. 12.1; 26.59.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino paiva pasina mvura yeungano\x + Eki. 17.1.\x*; zvino vakaunganira Mozisi naAroni\x + 16.19,42.\x*.
\v 3 Vanhu ndokupikisana naMozisi, ndokutaura, vachiti: Dai takafa\x + Eki. 17.2; Num. 14.2.\x* nguva yakafa hama dzedu pamberi paJehovha\x + 11.1,33; 14.37; 16.32,35,49.\x*!
\v 4 Makauisirei ungano yaJehovha murenje rino, kuti isu nezvipfuwo zvedu tifiremo\x + Eki. 17.3.\x*?
\v 5 Zvino makatikwidzirei kubva muEgipita, kutiuisa panzvimbo iyi yakaipa? Haizi nzvimbo yembeu kana yemaonde kana yemizambiringa kana yemapomegiranati*; uye hapana mvura yekunwa.
\v 6 Zvino Mozisi naAroni vakabva pamberi peungano kuenda kumukova wetende rekusangana ndokuwira pasi nezviso zvavo\x + 14.5; 16.4,22,45.\x*; kubwinya kwaJehovha ndokuonekwa kwavari\x + 14.10.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 8 Tora tsvimbo, ugounganidza ungano, iwe naAroni mukuru wako, mugotaura kudombo pamberi pemeso avo, zvino richapa mvura yaro, uye iwe\x + Eki. 17.5.\x* uchavabudisira mvura kubva padombo, kuti ugopa ungano nezvipfuwo zvavo zvinwe\x + Neh. 9.15. Isa. 43.20; 48.21.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino Mozisi wakatora tsvimbo kubva pamberi paJehovha sezvaakamuraira\x + 17.10.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino Mozisi naAroni vakaunganidza ungano pamberi pedombo, ndokuti kwavari: Inzwai ikozvino, imwi vapanduki, tichakubudisirai mvura kubva padombo iri here\x + Map. 106.32,33.\x*?
\v 11 Zvino Mozisi wakasimudza ruoko rwake, ndokurova dombo kaviri netsvimbo yake; mvura zhinji ndokudzatuka, ungano ikanwa, nezvipfuwo zvavo\x + Det. 8.15. Eki. 17.6.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni \add achiti\add*: Nokuti hamuna kunditenda\x + 27.14. Det. 1.37; 3.26; 32.51.\x*, kundiita mutsvene pameso evana vaIsraeri, naizvozvo hamungapinzi ungano iyi munyika yandakavapa\x + Eze. 20.41; 36.23; 38.16.\x*.
\v 13 Iyi imvura yeMeribha, nokuti vana vaIsraeri vakapikisana naJehovha; zvino akaitwa mutsvene mavari\x + Det. 33.8. Map. 81.7; 95.8; 106.32.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Mozisi wakatuma nhume kuna mambo weEdhomu\x + Gen. 36.39.\x* kubva kuKadheshi \add achiti\add*\x + Vato. 11.16,17.\x*: Ndizvo zvinoreva munin'ina wako Israeri: Iwe unoziva nhamo dzose dzakatiwira\x + Det. 2.4-6; 23.7. Obh. 10,12.\x*;
\v 15 kuti madzibaba edu akaburukira Egipita\x + Gen. 46.6. Mab. 7.15.\x*, uye takagara muEgipita mazuva mazhinji\x + Eki. 12.40.\x*, VaEgipita ndokutiitira zvakaipa isu nemadzibaba edu\x + Det. 26.6. Eki. 1.11; Mab. 7.19.\x*.
\v 16 Patakachema kuna Jehovha, wakanzwa inzwi redu\x + Eki. 2.23; 3.7.\x*, ndokutuma mutumwa ndokutibudisa paEgipita; zvino tarirai, tiri muKadheshi, guta riri pamucheto wemuganhu wenyika yako\x + Eki. 3.2; 14.19; 23.20; 33.2.\x*.
\v 17 Tirege hako tipfuure nepanyika yako; hatingaguri nepaminda, kana nepaminda yemizambiringa; uye hatinganwi mvura yematsime; tichafamba nenzira yamambo; hatingatsaukiri kurudyi kana kuruboshwe, kusvika tapfuura muganhu wako\x + 21.22. Det. 2.27.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino Edhomu wakati kwaari: Haungapfuuri nekwandiri, zvimwe ndingakubudira nemunondo.
\v 19 Vana vaIsraeri ndokuti kwaari: Tichafamba nenzira huru; uye kana ini nezvipfuwo zvangu tikanwa pamvura yako\x + 2 Zvak. 20.12,13. Isa. 11.16; 19.23.\x*, ipapo ndichapa mutengo wayo\x + Det. 2.6,28.\x*; koga ndichapfuura nemakumbo angu pasina chimwe.
\v 20 Iye ndokuti: Haungapfuuri. Zvino Edhomu wakamubudira nevanhu vazhinji uye neruoko rwune simba.
\v 21 Naizvozvo Edhomu akaramba kutendera Israeri kupfuura nepamuganhu wake\x + Det. 2.29.\x*. Ipapo Israeri wakatsauka kwaari\x + 21.4. Det. 2.8. Vato. 11.18.\x*.
\s Kufa kwaAroni
\p
\v 22 Zvino vana vaIsraeri, ungano yose, vakabva paKadheshi\x + 33.37.\x* vakasvika pagomo reHori\x + 21.4.\x*.
\v 23 Jehovha ndokutaura kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni mugomo reHori, pamucheto wenyika yaEdhomu, achiti:
\v 24 Aroni achaunganidzwa kuvanhu vake; nokuti haangapindi munyika yandakapa vana vaIsraeri\x + 27.13; 31.2. Det. 32.50,26. Gen. 25.8.\x*, nokuti makapandukira inzwi rangu pamvura yeMeribha\x + 20.12.\x*.
\v 25 Tora Aroni nemwanakomana wake Eriazari, ugovakwidza pagomo reHori.
\v 26 Zvino ukurure Aroni nguvo dzake, ugodzipfekedza Eriazari mwanakomana wake; zvino Aroni achaunganidzwa \add kuvanhu vake\add*, uye achafirapo\x + 20.24.\x*.
\v 27 Zvino Mozisi wakaita Jehovha sezvaakaraira; zvino vakakwira mugomo reHori pamberi pemeso eungano yose.
\v 28 Zvino Mozisi wakakurura Aroni nguvo dzake ndokudzipfekedza Eriazari mwanakomana wake\x + Eki. 29.29,30.\x*; Aroni ndokufirapo pamusoro pegomo; Mozisi naEriazari ndokuburuka mugomo\x + Det. 10.6; Det. 32.50.33.38.\x*.
\v 29 Zvino ungano yose yakati yaona kuti Aroni wafa, vakachemera Aroni mazuva makumi matatu, imba yose yaIsraeri\x + Det. 34.8. Gen. 50.3.\x*.
